OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAn
OL,6,Fincreasingly fine evening for many
OL,7,Fwith some sunshine but probably
OL,8,Fremaining cloudier across Cornwall
OL,9,Fwith mist and hill fog in places. Dry
OL,10,Fovernight with broken cloud and clear
OL,11,Fspells. Not as humid or warm as last
OL,12,Fnight. Winds easing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA fine, warm and sunny day
OL,15,Ffor most with the strong sunshine
OL,16,Fgiving very high UV levels. Much
OL,17,Flighter winds than on Friday, although
OL,18,Fsea breezes developing into the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
