OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry and
OL,6,Fvery warm on Sunday with hazy
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying mainly dry early
OL,8,Fnext week with occasional periods of
OL,9,Fstrong sunshine but also a chance of
OL,10,Fshowery rain at times.
